evidence.dc:description:
Growth on glycerol recovered for four types of revertants 

(1) same-site revertants;
(2) intragenic, second-site revertants; 
(3) tRNA Asp amplification revertants; and 
(4) nuclear suppressors


BUT The eight revertants which did not display temperature sensitivity had all recovered the Hinfl site indicating that they were same-site revertants in which the wild-type sequence was restored.
